high_descs: Turn right, proceed to table, turn right.  Proceed to tv stand.
Remove credit card from dresser under tv.
Turn around, proceed to table on right, turn right to face table.
Place credit card on table, to left of front statue.
Turn right, proceed to left side of tv stand.
Pick up credit card from dresser, to the right of the decorative plate.
Turn right, proceed to end of dresser.  Turn right, proceed to table on right, turn right to face table.
Place credit card on table, directly between other credit card and statue.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards from dresser to table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the middle of the large black dresser with the television on it.
Pick up the rightmost red credit card off of the dresser.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the side of the coffee table.
Put the red credit card onto the edge of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk over to the left side of the large black dresser.
Pick up the red credit card off of the dresser.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the side of the coffee table.
Put the red credit card on the coffee table to the right of the card that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two red credit cards to a coffee table.

high_descs: Walk over to the TV stand on the right.
Pick up the credit card in front of the TV.
Walk to the black coffee table.
Put the credit card down on the table in front of the remote.
Walk over to face the left side of the TV stand.
Pick up the credit card to the left of the TV.
Walk back over to the black coffee table.
Put the credit card down on the table to the left of the first credit card.
anns.task_desc: To move two credit cards to the coffee table.
